The HumanResources Application is an Enterprise Web Application designed and built for demonstration.

The application uses JSF and Primefaces for its Webpages and Application Views.

The WEB Controller, EJB and Persitence layers utilise Java CDI.

A MySQL database is used to persist the application data.

The application is fully unit tested using the following frameworks.

JUnit/Mocktio - Used for unit testing and mocking to provide a high level of test coverage.

Selenium - Used for full Application Integration testing, the selenium tests use the Page Objects design pattern.